  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BulkRetrievalEvent
    Notifies of bulk retrieval events.

    Provides an input handler that does nothing.

    SelectEvent
    This class signals that an object or terrain is under the cursor and identifies that object and the operation that caused the signal.
    WWEvent
    WWEvent is the base class which all World Wind event objects derive from.
